title: E51 Grateful Dead

description:
In this episode, the team discusses rock band Grateful Dead with their audiovisual archivist and legacy manager, David Lemieux.

Follow David on Twitter @LemieuxDavid and Grateful Dead on Twitter @GratefulDead
